OL,4,CHundreds more Afghans and their
OL,5,Cfamilies to be allowed to settle in UK
OL,6, Plans to rapidly relocate hundreds more
OL,7, Afghans who worked for the British
OL,8, military and UK government, mostly as
OL,9, interpreters, have been announced.
OL,11,FIncluding family members, more than
OL,12,F3,000 Afghans are expected to be
OL,13,Fallowed to settle in the UK, joining
OL,14,F1,300 who have already done so.
OL,16,FThe decision comes amid fears for their
OL,17,Fsafety as international troops prepare
OL,18,Fto leave the country.
OL,20,FDefence Secretary Ben Wallace said it
OL,21,Fwas "only right" to accelerate plans.
